rem Bum
rem 8/18/2017

do Ask About Night City
 [
  print "It's a ruff place. Came to Japan a few years ago, a hired gun for a 
  print biogenetics lab, but lost my job only to end up down here."
  setflag bum nightcity
 ]

ifflag bum job
 [
  do Ask About Job
   [
    ifflag bum hosaka
     [
      print "Not sure why they canned me. Someone up the ladder didn't like what I was 
      print doing."
     |
      print "Yeah, I worked in the biogenetics lab for Hosaka, it payed good before they
      print canned me."
      setflag bum hosaka
     ]
   ]
 |
  do Ask About Home
   [
    print "I live on the streets and sleep under the north bridge the conects us to
    print Harajuku. When I was working I lived in a cheap hotel south of here."
    setflag bum job
   ]
 ]

ifflag bum hosaka
 [
  do Ask About Hosaka
   [
    ifflag have badge
     [
      print "That place had tight securtiy when I worked there, good luck getting inside.
      print You might want to find a Fixer to arrange that D.N.A. for you."
     |
      print "That place had tight security when I worked there, you need an id badge to 
      print get in. I have my old one, but I doubt it works anymore."
      setflag know badge
     ]
   ]
 |]

do Ask About Alley
 [
  print "I'm not sure why they call it Ryders Alley, but I've always liked the name."
 ]

ifflag know badge
 [
  do Ask For Badge
   [
    ifflag bum trade
     [
      print "I told you I'll trade it for a pass into cheap hotel. I'm tired of sleeping
      print on the streets. Just one more night in a coffin is all ask for."
     |
      print "That's going to cost more than just new yen. Get me a pass back into cheap 
      print hotel and I'll trade it for the id badge."
      setflag bum trade
     ]
   ]
 |]

do End Conversation
 [
  print You mumble a few words of encouragement as you step away.
  go Ryders Alley
 ]